  "body": "TiKV has a switch to turn off the support for pessimistic transaction because it's an experimental feature in v3.x:\r\nhttps://github.com/tikv/tikv/blob/66feb3862ceb1c7eb3a29c13644ffce51a112be1/src/server/lock_manager/config.rs#L16\r\n\r\nAnd there are lots of annoying codes for it. For example, \r\nhttps://github.com/tikv/tikv/blob/66feb3862ceb1c7eb3a29c13644ffce51a112be1/cmd/src/server.rs#L430\r\nand \r\nhttps://github.com/tikv/tikv/blob/66feb3862ceb1c7eb3a29c13644ffce51a112be1/src/storage/txn/process.rs#L489\r\n\r\nNow it's the time to remove them all, but we should keep the configuration for the backward compatibility.",
